org.grouplens.lenskit.baseline

Annotation Type BaselineScorer


  • @Documented
@Qualifier
@DefaultNull
@Target(value={METHOD,PARAMETER})
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface BaselineScorer
    Annotation for the baseline scorer of a stacked item scorer, or an item scorer used as a baseline in another component. A baseline scorer should generally have full coverage (be able to predict for any item).
    Since:
    2.0
